application.controller

Class CashierController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.controller.CashierController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, javafx.event.EventHandler

    public class CashierController
extends Object
implements javafx.event.EventHandler
    The CashierController class controls the cashier's screen. This initializes all of the FXML buttons onto a matrix, makes an items ArrayList and a System instance.
    Author:
    Darean Wilde grl167 63678621, Jacob Shawver fww704 36242636, Majerus Sims hug180 79595196, Alexander Delgado tvh991 79595706
